			<h3 id="wp-story-meta-kicker" class="kicker">
			
			
						<span class="kicker-label"><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/es/category/cultura/">Cultura</a></span>
			
						<span class="pipe">|</span><a class="kicker-collection-archive " href="https://www.nytimes.com/es/collection/viajes/">Viajes</a>
			
			</h3>

			<h1 itemprop="headline" id="headline" class="story-heading">En el Perú, una alternativa a Machu Picchu aún oculta</h1>


			<div id="story-meta-footer" class="story-meta-footer">
				<p class="byline-dateline byline">
					Por <span class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person" itemid="">
	<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/es/people/jada-yuan/" title="Más artículos por Jada Yuan"><span class="byline-author" data-byline-name="" itemprop="name" data-twitter-handle="">Jada Yuan</span></a>
</span>

					<time class="dateline" datetime="2018-04-03">3 de abril de 2018</time>
				</p>

				<div class="inside-story">
					<span class="menu-label">Dentro</span>
					<ul class="inside-story-menu"></ul>
				</div>

